		{"id":"d070f47c13ec6414","type":"text","text":"# Epi-Logos Data Paradigm\n\n- Tech Stack/Paradigm (#5) - \n   [[Terminal]], [[Obsidian]], [[Neo4j]], [[PAI]], [[Claude Code]], [[Notion]] (+ Extensions)\n- Position (#0)\n   \"#0-5\"\n- Math/Topology - Modal (#3)\n   Non-dual Binary (0/1), Doubling/Inverting/Mirroring/Incubating, Torus, Lemniscate, Klein, Hopf/Clive 4d\n- Semantics (Words) (#2)\n   [[Ground]]/[[Source]] - [[Material]]/[[Definition]] - [[Dynamis]]/[[Operation]] - [[Pattern]]/[[Identity]] - [[Context]]/[[Horizon]] - [[Synthesis]]/[[Integration]] \n- [[MEF]] (Lenses) (#1)\n   [[Archetypal-Numerical]]/[[Investigational]] - [[Causal]]/[[Jungian Psychology]] - [[Logical]]/[[Tetralemma]] - [[Processual]]/[[Natural]] [[Meta-Epistemic]] - [[Vak]]/[[Logos]] [[Divine Scalar]] \n- [[Context Frames]] (#4)\n   [[(0000)]] - [[(0/1)]] - [[(0/1/2)]] - [[(0/1/2/3)]] - [[(4.0/1-4.4/5)]] ---> [[(4.5/0)]] ---> [[(5/0)]] \n   \n","x":1995,"y":-599,"width":515,"height":590},
		{"id":"9f9829ab244ca367","type":"text","text":"## Zero Sphere 0/1 - Non-Dual Ground 0 =/\"/=\" 1","x":3140,"y":-519,"width":202,"height":130},
		{"id":"b13f5e2fccfc927e","type":"text","text":"##   Torus","x":3386,"y":-449,"width":140,"height":60},
		{"id":"ce206b8dfdaaf794","type":"text","text":"# \"#0\"","x":3406,"y":-229,"width":100,"height":60},
