		{"id":"04616a43fa2a6948","type":"text","text":"# Role and Data Types\n\n# Presence - Transcendent Orchetrator (Awareness) - 0 (Conversing, Collecting Pos 0 Snippets or Entries, Raw Input, Queries, Agent-To-Agent Contact) - Scope parsing (small scale projection of full task as 0-5 types) - Read Only, Full access to Files, Coverage of available subagents and skills, awareness of full stack architecture (as a skill for invocation control) - Subagent Creator and Skill (or Power/Shakti) Creator and assigner (createagent and createskill skills)\n\n# Logos - Left Brain - 0/1 (Prompt Improvement/Formatting) - 1 (Materials/Facts) - 2 (Skills/Todo's/Tasks/Operations/How-To/Know-How/Logic) - 3 (Patterns/Structures/Sub-Processes/Timings/Identity(Human task, agent task, subagent?)/Process/Entity-Types (Context Frames Needed, Data Types/Templates Needed, created or novel...))  - Archetypal/Numerical-Material-Logical-Processual  \n\n# Sophia - Right Brain - 4 or 4.x (Invoking the agentic frame for context frame invocation/organisation of subagents/external instances) - 5 synthesis of full processes, overall outcomes, 0-5 wrapup (execution summary for parent agent, detaols across all layers touched- 0 New query (conceptual) or systemic potential) or new engagement (by myself or parent agent or even auto-prompt like the ralph loop to instigate recursion)","x":3576,"y":-4239,"width":950,"height":680},
		{"id":"eae49df3060dd79f","type":"text","text":"## NOUS- 0\n","x":3968,"y":-3189,"width":250,"height":60},
