		{"id":"50ec8eb318016164","type":"text","text":"4.0/1-4.4/5 = CP# (Agent Instance)\n00/00 = CF# (Session Instance, User context)","x":-8988,"y":3796,"width":220,"height":126},
		{"id":"a5076574937137ae","type":"text","text":"## The (00/00) is the user context and aligns with the overall 0-5 stack that the user engages with, which includes claude code - this class defines - CF = 0-3 = User to agent type processes, 4-5 = Agent to User\n\n## The (4.0/1-4.4/5) is the agent context, which includes the nested operations on the stack layers - CF' = 0-3 = Agent to User, 4-5 = User to agent\n\n## User - Journey - Unstructured Input -> Structured Reflection From agent (prompt improved, task detailed, implicit made explicit) -> Planning of tasks, details, what's not the case, considering tools, skills, subagents etc -> Mapping of process, timings, agent-to-user and user-to-agent junctures, diagrammatic organisation (canvas object organisation and embedded mermaids) -> Agent Runs, I do whatever, monitor, respond where needed, guide where needed, active in the moment learning loops potentiated, working within canvas as agents finish work and update our diagrammatic canvas web (adding notes and/or embedding full files) -> Tasks Complete and I review, look over for learnings in the summary, see what suggested loops or invocations are suggested, if tasks need to be run again (back to the 4\n\n","x":-9966,"y":3735,"width":787,"height":684},
		{"id":"3412f337e28af91b","type":"text","text":"---\n\n---\nSynthesis (Day)\n\nAnd Analysis (Night') \n\n40 Days 40 Nights\n\nCP# - Context Position - 4.#/#' - Data Entity types\n \nCF# Context Frame - (#/#) / (#'/#') - Session States/Frames - Presence vs Logos vs Sophia vs Eros\n\n# NARA?","x":-8459,"y":3899,"width":378,"height":351},
		{"id":"aa6f3c40283a8e5f","type":"text","text":"0000 -> 2222 = 80 days and nights plus 0000","x":-8433,"y":3693,"width":250,"height":60},
