		{"id":"61f70c80d1e6bf90","type":"text","text":"## (Mahamaya)- Klein\n\n## 2^6 = 64 bit encoding  (I-Ching)\n## 4 (2x2) x 16 (4x2)= 64\n\n## (4x2)^2\n\n## Codon Families","x":-5254,"y":3234,"width":297,"height":284},
